snippet.title: The Amber Guyger murder trial: Day 7
snippet.description:
The murder trial of Amber Guyger is set to resume today. Defense attorneys presented their case for about two hours on Saturday before jurors were dismissed for the weekend. Our live coverage of the trial continues with Tanya Eiserer and defense attorney Barry Sorrels. Court is scheduled to begin at 9:30 a.m. CST
 
BACKGROUND:

Former Dallas police officer Amber Guyger is on trial for murder after she fatally shot Botham Shem Jean on September 6, 2018.  

Guyger was off duty but still in uniform when she went into Jean's apartment at South Side Flats. She told investigators she believed she was walking into her own apartment and shot Jean believing he was an intruder. 

MORE: https://www.wfaa.com/bothamjean
